{"tid":2348892,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"麥玲玲預測牛年運程　寄語港人不要太悲觀：香港仍然有運勢","createTime":"2021-01-01T06:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T08:28:27.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5903dd427b249c1ef9e8b12897881c7485329447","tid":2348892,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:18:50.000Z","msg":"胡定欣、麥玲玲今日（31/12）現身銅鑼灣出席健康產品新店開幕儀式，來到2020年的最後一天，玲玲姐亦跟大家預測來年運勢。疫情肆虐了一段長時間，相信大眾非常關心疫情何時受控以及不用配戴口罩，玲玲姐指來年將會有好轉：「牛年係漸進式咁好，多勞多得嘅年份，唔會有突然間大反彈地好，期望秋天以後，所有嘢去返正常軌道。」<br />\n<br />\n對於2021年的寄語，玲玲姐望港人不要太悲觀：「香港仍然有運勢，牛只係比較辛苦嘅生肖，回報上冇以前咁多，但仍然係好嘅年份，去到老虎年會再好啲。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201231/421428226980581376841709.jpeg/EI4kVXxwz4jOHLCF3ZtiJiCH4c6VXlgKENEnoBDRJ6A?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201231%2F421428226980581376841709.jpeg%2FEI4kVXxwz4jOHLCF3ZtiJiCH4c6VXlgKENEnoBDRJ6A%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=ab74a0c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201231/421421453007654912764125.jpeg/Zht9SQzt0B1Z9ZJV53Udtr6asNaOrDh6eXQxukx0Mbo?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201231%2F421421453007654912764125.jpeg%2FZht9SQzt0B1Z9ZJV53Udtr6asNaOrDh6eXQxukx0Mbo%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=08332898&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87953917f85681198f9929f92dde80deb7e602ea","tid":2348892,"uid":224533,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:20:06.000Z","msg":"英女皇一生大富大貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302ea955cb1d581b28dd1fcffe2f318be44cf3af","tid":2348892,"uid":56701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:34:43.000Z","msg":"神棍"},{"pid":"78955766a9a683f99403c6dd56711970e7bd3b62","tid":2348892,"uid":226739,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T06:40:48.000Z","msg":"某年運程竟然用動物嘅習性黎比喻<img sr